  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Sustainable Energy and Carbon Finance Facility (SECFF), Russian Federation</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project supported the finance facility &#x2018;Sustainable Energy and Carbon Market&#x2019; set up by the European Bank for Reconstruction and Development (EBRD). Through this facility, the EBRD provided financing to local partner banks for credit lines for energy efficient measures. The project also carried out capacity-building in order to increase awareness for investment in energy efficient measures among participating banks and potential borrowers. Bank personnel was able to acquire competencies in risk assessment and the allocation of sustainable energy loans. Potential borrowers received support in identifying opportunities for energy conservation in their businesses.</narrative>
  </description>
